Richards Bay Coal Exports Rose 19% in June From Year Ago

-- B y   C a r l i   L o u r e n s
-- 
2011-07-07T11:31:33Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-07/richards-bay-coal-terminal-exports-rose-by-19-in-june-from-a-year-earlier.html
Shipments from Richards Bay Coal
Terminal, on  South Africa ’s east coast, rose 19 percent in June
from a year earlier, according to Bloomberg calculations based
on  data published  on the terminal’s website today.  -Editors: Alastair Reed,  Gordon Bell .  To contact the reporter on this story:
